br />\n我發覺啲大陸哩全部都係咁<br />\n有次係學校見到條大陸閪整爛啲私人物品同公家野<br />\n我影佢相佢話自己有肖像權要報警拉我 <br />\n我同佢講香港無肖像權佢又係話要告到我上中共人民法院 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbbd213003c6e610e3bad6e35362af4fdb235163","tid":491128,"uid":136994,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T08:50:29.000Z","msg":"屌<br />\n條廢老最後又反口申請保釋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20171206/s00001/1512546836839\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20171206%2Fs00001%2F1512546836839&d=RrWYVrTiYs3SVwhRt8KSZAEk2Noh57F05xbgvjQdsX8%3D&h=daa3726d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20171206%2Fs00001%2F1512546836839&h=5e5cbde1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20171206/s00001/1512546836839</a><br />\n<br />\n4名被告申請保釋等候上訴，獲裁判官批准。首被告、第2被告及第5被告以4000元保釋，每星期到警署報到。第4被告起初沒有申請，表示「我要上訴到中華人民共和國最高法院」，<span style=\"color: red;\">但經考慮後表示「我要去旅行，想保釋」，裁判官批准他以1500元保釋。</span>"},{"pid":"fe15bc240cf25763a530fc023beb9ea20b0e387a","tid":491128,"uid":62599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T08:51:30.000Z","msg":"幾廿歲人就唔好咁激動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n真係無眼睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係當年六七暴動 班老野年輕時期仲激<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41501479e8e49b398991a89b5c586e4b6d25ddc7","tid":491128,"uid":85163,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T08:59:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6028fbf9406e7fde5c58b6455deb79f5258e6a23","tid":491128,"uid":53498,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T09:01:05.000Z","msg":"入去死撚埋丫唔該"},{"pid":"2c81a950a2b861f1bb4a7bece10a7ff